com.deloitte.capi.cdm.executioncontrol

Class Source

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.deloitte.capi.cdm.executioncontrol.Source
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Source
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Overall POJO used for a "source" of data (e.g. Twitter). These objects are used to drive execution of the API, including amalgamation of the returned data, in both simple and detailed variants.
    Author:
    David Hunter (Deloitte)
